rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0001
rows.name: Gwin![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0002
rows.name:
Whoa—that was fast.
And you were so outnumbered and everything![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0003
rows.name: Nothing can stop Team Tatsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0004
rows.name: Tatsu eat baddies like them for breakfast![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0005
rows.name: Says tomorrow's breakfast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0006
rows.name: Colonel! Ma'am! Well done out there![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0007
rows.name:
Likewise. Now—what happened to Irina and Marcus?
Where are they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0008
rows.name: They're up checking on the Lifehold unit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0009
rows.name: And you've had no sign of hostiles?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0010
rows.name: No, dead quiet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0011
rows.name: Hmm, okay... It just felt so much like a...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0012
rows.name: A trap![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0013
rows.name: Irina! Marcus! RUN![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0014
rows.name: Hmm?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0015
rows.name: Marcus![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0016
rows.name: Right![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0041
rows.name: Ohh, what a shame. You didn't fall for my little surprise?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0042
rows.name: That voice... The woman from Noctilum?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0043
rows.name:
I knew they had to be holding back
their big guns for something. And here it is.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0044
rows.name: Well, aren't you the clever one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0045
rows.name:
What you just saw was only a prelude.
An amusement, if you will.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0046
rows.name: Blowing up our Lifehold...amuses you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0047
rows.name: Well, perhaps "amusement" is not quite the word.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0048
rows.name: More like, a deep satisfaction.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0049
rows.name: Like, curing an illness. Or scrubbing an ugly stain clean.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0050
rows.name: The stain of humanity.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0051
rows.name:
Of course, the true pleasure will come
from watching your real bodies burn...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0053
rows.name:
Not that I won't enjoy trashing these crude puppets of yours.
It'll certainly be enough to tide me over for the time being...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0054
rows.name: Till the real fun begins.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0055
rows.name: Then they know about the Lifehold and mims...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0056
rows.name: You primate. We know all about your kind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0057
rows.name: Your fool's errand to gather these trinkets.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0058
rows.name: Your race against time...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0059
rows.name: Human extinction is inevitable.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0060
rows.name:
I could simply wait for the clock to run out,
but where's the fun in that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0061
rows.name: I much prefer to see the looks on your faces.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0062
rows.name: How your features melt in fear as you twist in agony and—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0063
rows.name: That's enough—you Samaarian witch![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0064
rows.name:
Enough of your talk...
Enough of the pain you've caused the universe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0065
rows.name: The only agony...would be suffering you any longer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0066
rows.name: Oh, please. What would a mere human know of our history?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0067
rows.name: She is mine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0068
rows.name: Irina—your team has the others.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0069
rows.name: Right![ST:wait ]
